libs.content:
find_library (3rdparty_${upper_product_library_name}_library ${product_library_name}
                                         paths "${3rdparty_${upper_product_library_name}_library_dir}" "${3rdparty_tbb_dir}"
                                         path_suffixes bin
                                         cmake_find_root_path_both
                                         no_default_path)

deps.context: find_package(qt5 quiet components widgets quick xml paths ${3rdparty_qt_dir} no_default_path)

libs.content:
find_library (3rdparty_freetype_library ${csf_freetype}
                                              paths "${3rdparty_freetype_library_dir}" "${3rdparty_freetype_dir}"
                                              path_suffixes lib
                                              cmake_find_root_path_both
                                              no_default_path)

deps.context: find_package (x11 components x11 xext xmu xi)

libs.content:
find_library (3rdparty_ffmpeg_library_${library_name} names ${library_name}
                    paths "${3rdparty_ffmpeg_library_dir_${library_name}}" "${3rdparty_ffmpeg_dir}"
                    path_suffixes lib
                    cmake_find_root_path_both
                    no_default_path)

find_library (3rdparty_${product_name}_dll_${library_name_suffix} names ${library_name_suffix}
                                                             paths "${subdir_name}"
                                                             path_suffixes bin
                                                             no_default_path)
